Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils.color

Class MyShelfieAttribute

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.color.MyShelfieAttribute
Direct Known Subclasses:
ColorMyShelfieAttribute, SimpleMyShelfieAttribute
public abstract class MyShelfieAttribute extends Object
Abstracts ANSI codes with intuitive names. It maps a description (e.g. RED_TEXT) with a code (e.g. 31).
